See:
  http://screencasts.org/episodes/introduction-to-sinatra

install: 
   gem install sinatra
   gem install haml
   gem install shotgun

1. This version conatins the haml templates in the views/ directory

2. Version with layout file

3. Version with variables

= NOTES

With Sinatra, you can create a whole web application that lives in
one single, solitary ruby file.  Sinatra can use in-file templates.
In-file templates are added into the space after __END__ where each
view file is annotated with @@view_name.


